                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-57-victim615 t18301209-57-viclabel332"></join> - he has no partner. On the 25th of November, about half-past nine o'clock in the morning, I saw the prisoner in the shop; I saw him take this wooden box of cigars - I followed him; he put it down next door, finding himself followed - I pursued, and took him a very short distance from the door; he said he had not taken them, but I saw him taking them out of the shop - I did not see him enter.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18301209-57-person618">
                  ROBERT 
                  HOWARD
